      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways! You'll find it runs great and still looks sharp pullin' into the driveway. It\u2019s the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable, comfy ride that\u2019s ready for many more miles of memories. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 32500.0,
