    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Significant mechanical upkeep has been performed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed cooling system to manage thermal loads during spirited driving. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original suspension geometry to deliver precise turn-in and high-speed stability. An mechanically sound driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize performance over garage-queen status.",
      "price": 34500.0,
